            "title": "港股開市︱變動不大 恒指升5點報25780點 芯片股高開",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股今日是平安夜僅得半日市，大市開市初段微升，恒生指數開市報25780點，升5點或0.02%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5492點，升3點或0.07%；國企指數以8922點開市，升8點或0.09%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">芯片股高開，中芯國際(00981)開報70.35元，升2.1%；華虹半導體(01347)開報71.35元，也升1.49%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅科股普偏低開，阿里巴巴(09988)開報147元，跌0.14%；騰訊(00700)開報598元，跌0.66%；美團(03690)開報102.8元，跌0.39%；京東(09618)開報112.6元，跌0.18%；小米(01918)開報39.1元，跌0.26%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230704-174914_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230704-174914_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)持續強勢，今早開報122.6元，升0.25%；另一藍籌國際金融股友邦(01299)開報82.4元，跌0.3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">《2025年中國遊戲產業報告》顯示，中國遊戲收入全年料增長7.68%。網易(09999)今早高開，報215.4元，升1.22%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15532507-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e8%ae%8a%e5%8b%95%e4%b8%8d%e5%a4%a7-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%875%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b125780%e9%bb%9e-%e8%8a%af%e7%89%87%e8%82%a1%e9%ab%98%e9%96%8b",
